title: Mamma Mia Meatballs!
description: Classic Italian-style meatballs with Mediterranean flair. Amanda’s Creation  is a juicy, savoury meatballs bursting with Mediterranean flavour—every bite feels like a sun-soaked island escape!
creator: Amanda Lehan-Canto

title: Les MisBrûlée
description: A trio of Crème Brûlées inspired by Les Misérables, each representing a character. Keith attempted a rich, caramelized Crème Brûlée that sings of revolution and indulgence—liberté, égalité, délicatesse!
creator: Keith Leak Jr

title: My Fair Lady Fingers
description: A dainty tiramisu with class. Kimmy baked delicate ladyfingers layered with creamy mascarpone and coffee—refined and elegant, just like Eliza.
creator: Kimmy Jimenez

title: A Sound of Muesli
description: A fresh, harmonious breakfast medley of oats, fruit, and yoghurt. Shayne used a wholesome blend of oats, nuts, and fruit, harmonising like the hills in The Sound of Music.
creator: Shayne Topp

title: A Chorus Lime Tart
description: A zesty citrus tart with synchronised flavour. Angela made a zesty and sweet lime tart that hits all the right notes—an ensemble of flavour in every bite.
creator: Angela Giarratana

title: Dear Eclair Hansen
description: A sweet treat filled with vanilla and topped with theatre-blue icing. Chanse’s Creation Dear Eclair Hansen is inspired by Dear Evan Hansen.
creator: Chanse McCrary

title: And All That Deep Dish
description: A bold, indulgent pizza with a fiery kick. Trevor made a decadent, cheesy deep-dish pizza, oozing with flavour—Chicago’s finest!
creator: Trevor Evarts

title: Pasta La Vista, Dolly!
description: Creamy pasta with a theatrical garlic parmesan sauce. Saige made a hearty pasta dish that’s charming and classic—buon appetito!
creator: Saige Ryan Campbell

title: Technicolour veggie wrap
description: A rainbow veggie wrap bursting with colour. Tommy created a rainbow of crunchy veggies wrapped up in a soft tortilla, bursting with colour and freshness!
creator: Tommy Bowe

title: Grease Lightning Mac & Cheese
description: Extra cheesy, extra fast, extra nostalgic. Courtney ventured for a bold and creamy mac & cheese with a spicy twist—fast, fun, and unforgettable.
creator: Courtney Miller
